{"tid":2378361,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［桔梗］做實事被狗搞嘅黃店就嚟做唔住冇人講嘅， 人渣哥啲盆菜唔洗幾分鐘就賣哂喇","createTime":"2021-01-24T11:50:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T16:00:45.000Z","uid":237487,"like":43,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cfc26904e619dcb04392fa9e2fbde2b108308ce1","tid":2378361,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T11:50:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/jiegenge.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fjiegenge.hk%2F&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCPSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=7471a10a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/jiegenge.hk/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SnFNfZg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSnFNfZg.png&h=3d97b2ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514058c992f5bc0335dd140ad3f71400f9585e3f","tid":2378361,"uid":237487,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T11:51:55.000Z","msg":"【盆菜計劃不受影響，暫時停業後會重開】<br />\n-<br />\n收到各界仍然對本店的關注，在此澄清我們只是暫時停止營業，等待晚市和地區疫情受控再重開，多謝大家支持！<br />\n-<br />\n二月停業期間，我們仍然需要維持租金成本，會重新整理店鋪和主力銷售更多外賣及賀年產品。如果有興趣支持我們的同路人，可選擇下載 Lagom Kaffe Apps，訂購我們的【新年盆菜計劃】和【新年咖啡掛耳包禮盒】。同時，團隊正積極在海外開發更多賀年禮品，如有興趣訂購，可成為LagomKaffe會員並開啟上架通知，獲取我們最新資訊。<br />\n-<br />\n下載和購買鏈結：<br />\n盆菜預訂網址：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3hJCtAL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3hJCtAL&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCPSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=5cd7b993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3hJCtAL</a><br />\n2月6-7日加開場：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/391kAuK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F391kAuK&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCPSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=0900fde9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/391kAuK</a><br />\n新年咖啡掛耳包禮盒：稍後公佈<br />\n啡聞 咖啡掛耳包月費計劃：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/39b3Fpz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F39b3Fpz&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCPSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=0239ea9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/39b3Fpz</a><br />\n-<br />\n【牛頭角】和【觀塘】 Lagom Kaffe 樂感｜Not too Much Just Enough 姊妹分店會繼續正常營業。<br />\n-<br />\n祝大家身體健康，人人無事，共勉之。<br />\n-<br />\n地址：旺角砵蘭街160號地舖（創興廣場後面）<br />\nOpenRice: : <a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0Q8y4W0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS0Q8y4W0&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCPSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=189ea1fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0Q8y4W0</a><br />\n餐廳電話：27877328"},{"pid":"d37cf819782c2e84c550fcef3e13274bc057a08c","tid":2378361,"uid":388108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T11:58:20.000Z","msg":"想訂"},{"pid":"09fd699c090d329b10cb741e81c649e57c8b45f0","tid":2378361,"uid":237487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d37cf819782c2e84c550fcef3e13274bc057a08c","tid":2378361,"uid":388108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T11:58:20.000Z","msg":"想訂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T12:00:27.000Z","msg":"想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea9cd7a020841a51d49af6ea4a90c7971430514","tid":2378361,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T12:02:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab4aa6318e3fe39c37dded38cbc78f21cd92d69","tid":2378361,"uid":53922,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T12:03:40.000Z","msg":"有無黃店 盆菜list？"},{"pid":"a2d17f0aa35851230f724e9f0b0a100653d89802","tid":2378361,"uid":232228,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T12:04:09.0